nada más tenían que pedírmelo.</font>

788
00:55:09,475 --> 00:55:12,740
<font size="24">¡Por favor!
Eso es lo último que me interesa.</font>

789
00:55:12,812 --> 00:55:14,803
<font size="24">La princesa nada más estaba...</font>

790
00:55:19,751 --> 00:55:21,241
<font size="24">¡Ay!</font>

791
00:55:21,319 --> 00:55:25,221
<font size="24">Oiga, ¿qué es eso? ¿Es sangre?</font>

792
00:55:41,312 --> 00:55:44,974
<font size="24">♪ My beloved monster and me ♪</font>

793
00:55:46,249 --> 00:55:50,743
<font size="24">♪ We go everywhere together ♪</font>

794
00:55:50,854 --> 00:55:55,552
<font size="24">♪ Wearin'a raincoat
that has four sleeves ♪</font>

795
00:55:55,624 --> 00:56:00,254
<font size="24">- ♪ Gets us through all kinds of weather ♪
- Aah!</font>

796
00:56:00,329 --> 00:56:05,596
<font size="24">♪ She will always be
the only thing ♪</font>

797
00:56:05,668 --> 00:56:10,195
<font size="24">♪ That comes between me
and the awful sting ♪</font>

798
00:56:10,271 --> 00:56:15,334
<font size="24">♪ That comes from living in a worid
that's so damn mean ♪</font>

799
00:56:55,839 --> 00:56:57,739
